add

public boolean add(ListElement th)
Add the specified item to the list. Same as push. Will add the entry even if it is already in the list.

insert

public boolean insert(ListElement th)
Insert is like add except that it only adds once, i.e., if the entry already exists it returns false. So, two different instances of ListElement with the same value will not be allowed.

remove
